---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="de"
  title="&Uuml;bungsbibliothek - 240+ Krafttraining &Uuml;bungen - AIVancePro"
  description="Entdecken Sie unsere Bibliothek mit &uuml;ber 240 Krafttraining- und Fitness&uuml;bungen. Filtern Sie nach Muskelgruppe und finden Sie die perfekte &Uuml;bung."
  canonical="https://aivancepro.fr/de/uebungen/"
  alternates={{ fr: 'https://aivancepro.fr/exercices/', en: 'https://aivancepro.fr/en/exercises/', de: 'https://aivancepro.fr/de/uebungen/' }}
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <style>
        .page-header { padding: 9rem 2rem 2rem; text-align: center; background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-card), var(--bg)); }
        .section-label { display: inline-block; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
        .page-header h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .page-header p { color: var(--gray-500); font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 550px; margin: 0 auto; }

        .filter-bar { max-width: 1100px; margin: 2rem auto 0; display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; padding: 0 2rem; }
        .filter-btn { padding: 0.5rem 1.1rem; border-radius: 50px; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--bg-card); color: var(--gray-500); font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; font-family: inherit; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; }
        .filter-btn:hover, .filter-btn.active { background: var(--blue); color: var(--white); border-color: var(--blue); }

        .exercises-grid { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2.5rem 2rem 4rem; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.25rem; }

        .exercise-card { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.25rem; transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; }
        .exercise-card:hover { border-color: rgba(37,99,235,0.25); transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        .exercise-card .card-image { width: 100%; height: 140px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gray-100), var(--gray-200)); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: var(--gray-400); font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .exercise-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
        .exercise-card .tags { display: flex; gap: 0.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .exercise-card .tag { padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 600; }
        .tag-muscle { background: rgba(37,99,235,0.08); color: var(--blue); }
        .tag-compound { background: rgba(147,51,234,0.08); color: var(--purple); }
        .tag-isolation { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.08); color: #D97706; }
        .exercise-card p { color: var(--gray-500); font-size: 0.8rem; line-height: 1.5; }

        .exercises-count { text-align: center; padding: 1rem 2rem 0; color: var(--gray-400); font-size: 0.85rem; }

        .cta-section { padding: 5rem 2rem; text-align: center; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark), #1a1145); color: var(--white); }
        .cta-section h2 { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .cta-section p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size: 1rem; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
        .btn-primary { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--purple)); color: var(--white); text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 0.875rem 2rem; border-radius: 12px; transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(37,99,235,0.3); }
        .btn-primary:hover { opacity: 0.92; transform: translateY(-2px); }

        @media (max-width: 1024px) { .exercises-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .page-header { padding: 7rem 1.5rem 2rem; }
            .page-header h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
            .exercises-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
  </Fragment>

    <header class="page-header">
        <div class="section-label">&Uuml;bungen</div>
        <h1>&Uuml;bungsbibliothek</h1>
        <p>&Uuml;ber 240 &Uuml;bungen mit detaillierten Anleitungen. Filtern Sie nach Muskelgruppe, um die perfekte &Uuml;bung f&uuml;r Sie zu finden.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="filter-bar">
        <button class="filter-btn active" onclick="filterExercises('all', this)">Alle</button>
        <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterExercises('brust', this)">Brust</button>
        <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterExercises('ruecken', this)">R&uuml;cken</button>
        <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterExercises('schultern', this)">Schultern</button>
        <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterExercises('arme', this)">Arme</button>
        <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterExercises('beine', this)">Beine</button>
        <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterExercises('bauch', this)">Bauch</button>
        <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterExercises('cardio', this)">Cardio</button>
    </div>

    <div class="exercises-count"><span id="count">24</span> &Uuml;bungen angezeigt</div>

    <section class="exercises-grid">
        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="brust"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Bankdr&uuml;cken Foto</div><h3>Bankdr&uuml;cken</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">Brust</span><span class="tag tag-compound">Compound</span></div><p>Der K&ouml;nig der Brust&uuml;bungen. Trainiert auch Trizeps und vordere Schultern.</p></div>
        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="brust"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Schr&auml;gbankdr&uuml;cken Foto</div><h3>Schr&auml;gbankdr&uuml;cken</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">Brust</span><span class="tag tag-compound">Compound</span></div><p>Zielt auf die obere Brust ab. Ideal f&uuml;r die Entwicklung des oberen Brustbereichs.</p></div>
        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="brust"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Kurzhantel-Flyes Foto</div><h3>Kurzhantel-Flyes</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">Brust</span><span class="tag tag-isolation">Isolation</span></div><p>Isoliert die Brust mit einer &Ouml;ffnungsbewegung. Hervorragend f&uuml;r Dehnung und Kontraktion.</p></div>
        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="brust"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Dips Foto</div><h3>Dips</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">Brust</span><span class="tag tag-compound">Compound</span></div><p>Eigengewichts&uuml;bung f&uuml;r Brust und Trizeps. Neigungswinkel variieren f&uuml;r unterschiedliche Belastung.</p></div>

        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="ruecken"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Klimmz&uuml;ge Foto</div><h3>Klimmz&uuml;ge</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">R&uuml;cken</span><span class="tag tag-compound">Compound</span></div><p>Grundlegende R&uuml;cken&uuml;bung. Baut Latissimus-Breite und Bizepskraft auf.</p></div>
        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="ruecken"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Langhantelrudern Foto</div><h3>Langhantelrudern</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">R&uuml;cken</span><span class="tag tag-compound">Compound</span></div><p>Baut R&uuml;ckendicke auf. Zielt auf Rhomboide, Trapezius und Latissimus ab.</p></div>
        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="ruecken"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Kreuzheben Foto</div><h3>Kreuzheben</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">R&uuml;cken</span><span class="tag tag-compound">Compound</span></div><p>Die vollst&auml;ndigste &Uuml;bung. Beansprucht R&uuml;cken, Beine, Ges&auml;&szlig; und Rumpf.</p></div>
        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="ruecken"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Latzug Foto</div><h3>Latzug</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">R&uuml;cken</span><span class="tag tag-compound">Compound</span></div><p>Kabel-Alternative zu Klimmz&uuml;gen. Erm&ouml;glicht pr&auml;zise Gewichtsanpassung.</p></div>

        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="schultern"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Schulterdr&uuml;cken Foto</div><h3>Schulterdr&uuml;cken</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">Schultern</span><span class="tag tag-compound">Compound</span></div><p>Prim&auml;re Schulter&uuml;bung. Trainiert Deltamuskeln und Trizeps.</p></div>
        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="schultern"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Seitheben Foto</div><h3>Seitheben</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">Schultern</span><span class="tag tag-isolation">Isolation</span></div><p>Isoliert den seitlichen Deltamuskel f&uuml;r breitere Schultern. Bewegung kontrollieren.</p></div>
        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="schultern"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Face Pull Foto</div><h3>Face Pull</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">Schultern</span><span class="tag tag-isolation">Isolation</span></div><p>Zielt auf den hinteren Deltamuskel und Au&szlig;enrollatoren ab. Unverzichtbar f&uuml;r die Schultergesundheit.</p></div>

        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="arme"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Bizeps-Curl Foto</div><h3>Bizeps-Curl</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">Arme</span><span class="tag tag-isolation">Isolation</span></div><p>Die klassische Bizeps&uuml;bung. Varianten: Langhantel, Kurzhantel, Hammer.</p></div>
        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="arme"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Trizepsdr&uuml;cken Foto</div><h3>Trizepsdr&uuml;cken</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">Arme</span><span class="tag tag-isolation">Isolation</span></div><p>Isoliert den Trizeps mit Kabel oder Kurzhanteln. Ideale Erg&auml;nzung zu Dr&uuml;ck&uuml;bungen.</p></div>
        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="arme"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Hammer-Curl Foto</div><h3>Hammer-Curl</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">Arme</span><span class="tag tag-isolation">Isolation</span></div><p>Zielt auf Brachioradialis und Brachialis ab. Neutraler Griff f&uuml;r dickere Arme.</p></div>

        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="beine"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Kniebeuge Foto</div><h3>Kniebeuge</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">Beine</span><span class="tag tag-compound">Compound</span></div><p>Der K&ouml;nig der Bein&uuml;bungen. Trainiert Quadrizeps, Ges&auml;&szlig; und hintere Oberschenkel.</p></div>
        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="beine"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Ausfallschritte Foto</div><h3>Ausfallschritte</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">Beine</span><span class="tag tag-compound">Compound</span></div><p>Hervorragende unilaterale &Uuml;bung f&uuml;r Gleichgewicht, Quadrizeps und Ges&auml;&szlig;.</p></div>
        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="beine"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Beinpresse Foto</div><h3>Beinpresse</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">Beine</span><span class="tag tag-compound">Compound</span></div><p>Maschinen-Alternative zur Kniebeuge. Erm&ouml;glicht schweres Laden mit Sicherheit.</p></div>
        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="beine"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Beincurl Foto</div><h3>Beincurl</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">Beine</span><span class="tag tag-isolation">Isolation</span></div><p>Isoliert die hintere Oberschenkelmuskulatur. Unverzichtbar f&uuml;r das muskul&auml;re Gleichgewicht der Beine.</p></div>
        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="beine"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Hip Thrust Foto</div><h3>Hip Thrust</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">Beine</span><span class="tag tag-compound">Compound</span></div><p>Die beste Ges&auml;&szlig;&uuml;bung. H&uuml;ftstreckung mit progressiver &Uuml;berlastung.</p></div>

        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="bauch"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Crunch Foto</div><h3>Crunch</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">Bauch</span><span class="tag tag-isolation">Isolation</span></div><p>Grundlegende Bauch&uuml;bung. Fokus auf die Kontraktion des geraden Bauchmuskels.</p></div>
        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="bauch"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Plank Foto</div><h3>Plank</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">Bauch</span><span class="tag tag-isolation">Isolation</span></div><p>Isometrische Rumpfkr&auml;ftigung. Verbessert allgemeine Stabilit&auml;t und Haltung.</p></div>
        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="bauch"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">H&auml;ngendes Beinheben Foto</div><h3>H&auml;ngendes Beinheben</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">Bauch</span><span class="tag tag-isolation">Isolation</span></div><p>Zielt auf die unteren Bauchmuskeln ab. An einer Stange h&auml;ngen f&uuml;r maximalen Bewegungsumfang.</p></div>

        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="cardio"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Ruderger&auml;t Foto</div><h3>Ruderger&auml;t</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">Cardio</span><span class="tag tag-compound">Compound</span></div><p>Ganzk&ouml;rper-Cardio, das den gesamten K&ouml;rper beansprucht. Hervorragendes Aufwand-zu-Gelenkbelastung-Verh&auml;ltnis.</p></div>
        <div class="exercise-card" data-muscle="cardio"><div class="card-image img-placeholder">Seilspringen Foto</div><h3>Seilspringen</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag tag-muscle">Cardio</span><span class="tag tag-compound">Compound</span></div><p>Hochintensives Cardio und Koordination. Perfekt zum Aufw&auml;rmen oder f&uuml;r HIIT.</p></div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
        <h2>240+ &Uuml;bungen in Ihrer Tasche</h2>
        <p>Laden Sie AIVancePro herunter, um auf alle &Uuml;bungen mit Videos, Anleitungen und direkter Integration in Ihre Workouts zuzugreifen.</p>
        <a href="https://apps.apple.com/app/aivancepro/id6756116760" class="btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Kostenlos herunterladen</a>
    </section>

    <script>
        function filterExercises(muscle, btn) {
            document.querySelectorAll('.filter-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
            btn.classList.add('active');
            let count = 0;
            document.querySelectorAll('.exercise-card').forEach(card => {
                if (muscle === 'all' || card.dataset.muscle === muscle) {
                    card.style.display = '';
                    count++;
                } else {
                    card.style.display = 'none';
                }
            });
            document.getElementById('count').textContent = count;
        }
    </script>
</BaseLayout>
